OpenCL-OCaml Readme

Table of Contents
------------------
1. Overview
2. Building



1. Overview
------------------
OpenCL-OCaml is OCaml binding for OpenCL.  It currently has implemented the most
important OpenCL calls.  See examples for usage.


2. Building
------------------
To build the library do:

    make

If OpenCL library cannot be found modify Makefile's OPENCL_LIB_DIR.

To build examples and documentation do:

    make examples
    make doc